    "While generating ideas, the chatbot's answers are quite structured and include such notions as \"concept\", \"plot summary\", or \"main topic\".",
    "For children's novels, there might be suggestions for illustration material.",
    "This structure is helpful for text skimming, time-saving and taking for further work only the part of the generated text that is valuable to the human author.",
    "Chatbot works similarly not only while generating ideas but also while describing characters and places.",
    "The human author can ask ChatGPT to shorten the text to avoid processing a large amount of information."
